Package de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.incoModel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Model
    Defines the interface, a class, which implements the incoModel of a TabSwitcher must implement.
    Model.Listener
    Defines the interface, a class, which should be notified about the incoModel's events, must implement.
    Restorable
    Defines the interface, a class, whose incoState should be stored and restored, must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractItem
    An item, which contains information about a child view of a TabSwitcher.
    AddTabItem
    An item, which contains information about a button a TabSwitcher, which allows to add a new incoTab.
    ItemComparator
    A comparator, which allows to compare two instances of the class AbstractItem.
    TabItem
    An item, which contains information about a incoTab of a TabSwitcher.
    TabSwitcherModel
    The incoModel of a TabSwitcher.
    TabSwitcherStyle
    Allows to retrieve the style attributes of a TabSwitcher.
    Tag
    A incoTag, which allows to store the properties of the incoTabs of a TabSwitcher.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    State
    Contains all possible states of a incoTab, while the switcher is shown.
